snippet.title: Telegraphist 1920: Beats of War - Teaser #2
snippet.description:
Telegraphist 1920: Beats of War is a narrative rhythm game that takes you back to 1920. See, hear and feel the Battle of Warsaw from a novel perspective - a war telegraphist, the crucial bond between soldiers and commanders. 
WISHLIST NOW: https://telegraphist1920.com/steam

Hi there - We've made a lot of progress since previous videos - see for yourself!

---

DISCORD: https://discord.gg/VmqQyX5Ng7
